            "body": "I'd also like to see this. Neovim users seem like the perfect audience for Cursorless given how it allows you to manipulate text. \r\n\r\nOn top of that using Cursorless with Talon Voice can reduce the number of hotkeys you need to remember - or just give you more convenient ways to navigate nvim.",
